Add or remove rows as the project's tooling evolves. Keep it short — full task definitions live in the project's actual task file (`Makefile`, `Taskfile.yml`, `package.json` scripts, etc.).

## Workflow

Every session starts with `/prime`, which is auto-triggered by the plugin's SessionStart hook. To plan new work: `/plan <feature-name>`. To resume open work: `/continue`.

See the plugin's [README](https://github.com/{{plugin_repo}}) for the full 8-phase workflow and command reference.
